  <additions>
  <list>
  <item xml:id="a1">
  <locus from="2v"/>
  <desc type="GuestText"><title type="complete">A short chronological section from Adam to Christ, in Amharic.</title></desc>
  <q xml:lang="am"><seg part="F">ዘንተ፡ ዘአጽሐፈ፡ <persName role="patron" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13283SahlaMikael">ሣህለ፡ ሚካኤል፡</persName> <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC5662Semada">ዘስማዳ</placeName>፡ ወዘጸሐፈ፡
  <persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13284GabraIyasus">ገብረ፡ ኢየሲስ፡</persName> ዘ<placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC6563Sada">ፀዳ፡</placeName> ዘተቀብረ፡ ቦቱ፡ ጻድቅ፡ <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10375Yohanne">ዮሐንስ፡</persName> ንጉሠ፡ ነገሥት፡
  አንቢበክሙ፡ እንዘ፡ ትፌጽሙ፡ ፩አቡነ፡ ዘበሰማያት፡ በእንተ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ አብ።</seg></q>
  </item>

  <item xml:id="a2">
    <locus target="#4r"/>
    <desc type="OwnershipNote">The note states that the manuscript belongs to the church of <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0101MadhaneAlam">Madḫāne ʿAlam</placeName>
    </desc>
    <q xml:lang="gez">ስንክሳር፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ መድኃኔ፡ ዓለም።</q>
  </item>

  <item xml:id="a3">
  <locus target="#2r"/>
  <locus from="220v" to="221r"/>
  <desc type="GuestText"><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2870RepCh151">Hymn to John the Baptist.</title></desc>
  <q xml:lang="gez"><seg part="I">ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ዘበመጽሐፈ፡ ሕግ፡ ተሐተመ፡ ወለሰዕርትከ፡ ሜላት፡ ዘእምፈትለ፡ ሥጋ፡ ተአንመ፡</seg></q>
  <note>The attribution of the hymn to John the Baptist is based on <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/MIFKZCUN"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Wright1877BM"/><title level="m">Catalogue of the Ethiopic Manuscripts in the British Museum Acquired since the Year 1847</title><author><forename>William</forename><surname>Wright</surname></author><pubPlace>London</pubPlace><publisher>Gilbert and Rivington</publisher><date>1877</date><note type="url">https://archive.org/details/catalogueofethio00brituoft</note><note type="tags"><note type="tag">bm:Wright1877BM</note><note type="tag">British Museum</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note></note><note type="tag">bm:Wright1877BM</note><note type="tag">British Museum</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note></bibl>. However according to
<bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/7WA33SUX"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Chaine1913Rep"/><title level="a">Répertoire des Salam et Malkeʾe contenus dans les manuscrits éthiopiens des bibliothèques d’Europe</title><title level="j">Revue de l’Orient Chrétien</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Marius</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Chaîne</t:surname></author><date>1913</date><biblScope unit="volume">18</biblScope><biblScope unit="issue">2 and 4 (Deuxième série, 8/2 and 8/4)</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">183–203 and 337–357</biblScope><note type="url">http://catholicapedia.net/Documents/Revue-de-l.Orient-chretien/18-1913_revue-de-l.orient-ch_paris.pdf</note></bibl> it is addressed to John the Evangelist, whereas
<bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/IHMFEASA"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:EMML7"/><title level="m">A Catalogue of Ethiopian Manuscripts Microfilmed for the Ethiopian Manuscript Microfilm Library, Addis Ababa, and for the Hill Monastic Manuscript Library, Collegeville, VII: Project Numbers 2501–3000</title><author><name>Getatchew Haile</name></author><author><forename>William F.</forename><surname>Macomber</surname></author><pubPlace>Collegeville, MN</pubPlace><publisher>Hill Monastic Manuscript Library, St. John's Abbey and University</publisher><date>1983</date><note type="url">https://archive.org/details/EMMLCatalog07</note><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">EMML</note><note type="tag">bm:EMML7</note></note><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">EMML</note><note type="tag">bm:EMML7</note><citedRange unit="page">104-105</citedRange></bibl>ascribes it to emperor <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10375Yohanne">Yoḥannǝs I</persName>.</note>
  </item>

  <item xml:id="e1">
  <locus target="#2r"/>
  <desc type="MixedNote">The name of ʾabbā <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13284GabraIyasus">Gabra ʾIyasus</persName> is on f. 2r.</desc>
  </item>

  </list>
  </additions>

